description.displayText: Tricia, sat for us with our newborn (8wks) and was excellent.  It is refreshing to find a mature babysitter who is friendly and caring.  We highly recommend her.

description.displayText:
Tricia has been a Godsend to our family!  I have four children, ages 11, 9, 6 and 1 year. She started watching my 1 year old during the day while the other three were at school and did a great job with the baby.  On nights when she's had all of my kids, I have not had a single worry that they weren't being taken care of.  They always have enjoyed their time with her, since she plays lots of games with them.  She communicates really well when she isn't going to be available and is always on time.  I couldn't ask for a better, more trustworthy babysitter.
Thank you Tricia!

description.displayText: Tricia has been wonderful with our children, they absolutely love her.  She has been very flexible and willing to work with us when we need her. We recommend her to anyone!

description.displayText: Tricia worked for us for 2 months as a regular nanny Monday-Friday. Our daughter (6 months at the time) loved her! Tricia was always willing to go above and beyond anything that we asked of her. Our daughter even started signing the word "milk" while under Tricia's care. She is very friendly, honest and anyone who hires her is lucky to have her. If she hadn't moved, we would have loved to still have her working for us!
